@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.PASTE_YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### ──────────────────────────────────────
### 권한 목록 조회
### ──────────────────────────────────────

### 1. 권한 목록 조회 (기본 page=1, limit=10) → 200
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/permissions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 1-1. 권한 목록 조회 (페이징: 1페이지, 5개) → 200
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/permissions?page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 1-2. 권한 목록 조회 (통합검색: 아이디) → 200
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/permissions?search=admin
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 1-3. 권한 목록 조회 (통합검색: 이름) → 200
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/permissions?search=관리자
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 1-4. 권한 목록 조회 (통합검색 + 페이징) → 200
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/permissions?search=admin&page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. 토큰 없이 조회 → 401
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/permissions

### ──────────────────────────────────────
### 건물 할당
### ──────────────────────────────────────

### 3. 건물 할당 - 정상 요청 (사용자 seq=2에 건물 1,2 할당) → 200
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/permissions/2/buildings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "buildingSeqs": [1, 2]
}

### 3-1. 건물 할당 - 단일 건물 할당 → 200
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/permissions/2/buildings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "buildingSeqs": [1]
}

### 3-2. 건물 할당 - 전체 해제 (빈 배열) → 200
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/permissions/2/buildings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "buildingSeqs": []
}

### 3-3. 건물 할당 - 존재하지 않는 건물 → 404
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/permissions/2/buildings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "buildingSeqs": [9999]
}

### 3-4. 건물 할당 - 존재하지 않는 사용자 → 404
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/permissions/99999/buildings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "buildingSeqs": [1]
}

### 3-5. 건물 할당 - 토큰 없이 → 401
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/permissions/2/buildings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "buildingSeqs": [1]
}

### 3-6. 건물 할당 - 잘못된 body → 400
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/permissions/2/buildings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "buildingSeqs": "invalid"
}
